User Guide（运行说明）
Library Book Graph – User Guide
How to Run the Program
Make sure you have Python 3 installed on your computer.
Download the Python file library_book_graph.py.
Open a terminal or command prompt in the same folder.
Run the program using:
python library_book_graph.py
The output will show:
Each book with its ID and title
Connected books and co-borrow weight
Program Features
Add books with ID, title, author
Record co-borrowed book pairs
Automatically update relationship strength (weight)
Display the full book relationship network
Test Case Explanation
